{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A tower defense game with a city-building element!\u00a0 Voices, alien attributes, and attack patterns are all varied and randomized each game so that each experience is a unique one!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Operating from behind your radar screen, in this monochromatic display, you'll direct the special ops units to construct towers in the locations you choose.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234980/extras/BuildTowerClip.gif?t=1736862173\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Keep an eye on your power, support, and supply, as every new build will use and require your available resources.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234980/extras/ResourcesClip.gif?t=1736862173\" />\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you run short of supplies, power, or support, you'll need to construct (anywhere you'd like) additional  structures to the base you are trying to defend from alien invaders.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234980/extras/BuildStructureClip.gif?t=1736862173\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> In a game driven by audio over visuals, you'll get check-ins and updates from your facilities and units, make decisions on how best to build up a basic defense, and learn more about the attackers to improve defensive capabilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234980/extras/IncomingCallClip.gif?t=1736862173\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_pa